title: Hunan Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, Delivery, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Food is advertised as no MSG, low sodium, fresh veggies, and no microwaves. There is a steamed vegetable lunch special with veggie roll or egg roll, Indian curry with tofu and vegetable, red curry, kung pao tofu, and moo shu vegetables. Will make a dish vegetarian/vegan upon request. Fast service. Dishes are mild in spice and you could ask for more spicy.
